description: Hedera Group AB engages in the provision of recruiting and staffing services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 29 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2013-05-30. The firm is focused on acquisitions within healthcare industry. The firm along with its subsidiaries provides staffing and recruitment services in Sweden. The firm operates through such subsidiaries as LakarResurs FA Rekryt AB, Svensk lakartjanst LIL AB, Pridoc Bemanning AB, among others. LakarResurs FA Rekryt AB provides staffing of doctors to the County Council in Sweden. Svensk lakartjanst LIL AB offers staffing services for public and private healthcare providers. Pridoc Bemanning AB is involved in the medical personnel recruitment and specializes in primary care and psychiatry.
